These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
Music-Genre: punk, hip-hop, house, ambient
1. Music-Genre:ambient is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
2. Beverage:7up is on the left of Music-Genre:hip-hop##1
3. Beverage:water is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:house is on the left or right of Music-Genre:ambient##3
5. Beverage:7up is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | coffee | water | lemonade |
| Music-Genre        | punk | hip-hop   | ambient | house    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
City: hamburg, nizza, miami, paris
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. City:hamburg is on the left of City:miami##1
3. City:miami is in an odd position##4
4. City:hamburg == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. City:nizza is on the right of City:miami##1
6. City:hamburg == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| City   | paris    | hamburg | miami | nizza    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: singing, collecting, gardening, camping
Movie-Genre: animation, documentary, spy, western
1. Hobby:camping is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:western##3
2. Hobby:gardening is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:western is on the left or right of Hobby:collecting##3
4. Movie-Genre:western is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:animation is in an odd position##4
6. Hobby:collecting is on the right of Hobby:gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Hobby          | camping | gardening | collecting    | singing      |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | western     | animation | documentary |

