.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Pet: hedgehog, pony, bird, fish
Nationality: american, australian, indian, russian
1. Pet:bird is on the right of Nationality:russian##1
2. Nationality:australian == Pet:fish##1
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Pet:hedgehog##1
4. Pet:pony is on the far left##1
5. Pet:bird is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Pet   | pony  | hedgehog    | bird   | fish       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

