3. Music-Genre:punk is on the left of Music-Genre:metal##1
4. Transport:ship == Music-Genre:jazz##1
5. Music-Genre:punk is on the left or right of Transport:car##3
6. Transport:quad-bike is on the right of Transport:car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | punk | metal | house    |
| Transport     | ship | roller  | car     | quad-bike |

