4. Job:teacher is on the right of House:tower##1
5. Job:coach is between Job:teacher and Job:pilot##2
6. House:palace is in an odd position##4
7. House:palace is between Job:coach and House:ranch-style##2
8. Job:coach is on the left or right of Job:pilot##3

