.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
Food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
Game: backgammon, poker, bridge, domino
1. Food:pepper is on the left or right of Food:cabbage##3
2. Food:cabbage is on the right of Food:mango##1
3. Game:backgammon is between Game:poker and Food:pepper##2
4. Game:backgammon is in an odd position##4
5. Food:pepper == Game:bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Game    | domino     | poker | backgammon     | bridge  |

