.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
Cigar: bongani, game, baccarat, prince
1. Beverage:almond-milk == Cigar:prince##1
2. Cigar:bongani is on the right of Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Cigar:prince is between Cigar:bongani and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. Cigar:prince is on the left or right of Cigar:bongani##3
6. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Cigar:game##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Cigar   | baccarat | game | prince        | bongani    |

