2. Sport:ice-hockey == City:miami##1
3. Sport:cricket == City:hannover##1
4. City:edinburgh is on the left or right of City:hannover##3
5. City:miami is in an even position##4
6. City:edinburgh is on the right of Sport:ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| City   | hamburg | miami | edinburgh    | hannover |
| Sport   | basketball   | ice-hockey  | water-polo | cricket     |

