.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Game: canasta, backgammon, monopoly, chess
Food: corn, kale, pepper, strawberry
1. Food:kale is on the far left##1
2. Game:monopoly is on the left or right of Game:canasta##3
3. Game:chess is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:pepper is on the left of Food:strawberry##1
5. Food:strawberry is on the right of Game:canasta##1
6. Food:pepper is in an even position##4
7. Food:corn == Game:backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Game   | chess | canasta    | monopoly       | backgammon |
| Food       | kale  | pepper | strawberry | corn  |

